text: Hey, there was a matte painting competition on the discord, matte painting isn't my strongest thing but I thought I would give it a go.

Yes, you should.

Also, yesterday and today, there is the first edition of the Real-TIme conference. There are lots of great speakers. This afternoon there will be lots of conferences about digital humans. If you register, you will also have access to yesterday's conferences about virtual production. It was supposed to be a very expensive conference, but due to the coronavirus, it has become fully online and free.

<https://realtimeconference.com/registration/>
